Dear Khaled,

 

I hope this email finds you well.

 

We now have submitted a PR # 8471107698 for Lumerial software license renewal (which expired in late March) after having access to the approved budget.

 

The vendor has agreed to provide a loan of our license time provided we notify them of the approximate date of the expected PO.

 

Is it possible to commit a date to the vendor to issue us the loan license?

 

Best Regards, 

Abdul Lateef

+971 2 312 3585

 

