Sent: Thursday, March 25, 2021 1:42 PM
To: Abdul Lateef Khan <abdullateef.khan@ku.ac.ae>
Cc: Ahmed Al Yafei <ahmed.alyafei@ku.ac.ae>
Subject: Re: Lumerical license renewal

 

Dear Abdul Lateef,

 

Thanks for the follow up.

 

If possible, can you please get in touch with the procurement department to get them to commit to completing this within the 4 weeks. If they do, please get Catriona to issue the loan license based on that  date.

 

Thanks,

Dureid

 

P.S. I received and approved the PR this morning, there is one final approval remaining from SVP of research. Let me know if it is not done end of day.

 

 

 

